Keluar!

00:05:58.000 --> 00:05:59.360
Mama!

00:05:59.800 --> 00:06:01.200
Hai!  Chintu!

00:06:02.800 --> 00:06:03.760
Ibu mertua!

00:06:05.640 --> 00:06:08.680
